public interface IEnquiryService

  • Method Details

    • getProjectEnquiries

      List<Enquiry> getProjectEnquiries(Project project)
      Retrieves all enquiries submitted for a specific project.
      Parameters:
      project - The project for which to retrieve enquiries.
      Returns:
      A list of enquiries related to the given project.

    • getEnquiriesByApplicant

      List<Enquiry> getEnquiriesByApplicant(Applicant applicant)
      Retrieves all enquiries made by a specific applicant.
      Parameters:
      applicant - The applicant whose enquiries are to be retrieved.
      Returns:
      A list of enquiries submitted by the applicant.

    • createEnquiry

      void createEnquiry(Enquiry enquiry)
      Submits a new enquiry.
      Parameters:
      enquiry - The enquiry to create.

    • editEnquiry

      void editEnquiry(Applicant applicant, String enquiryId, String newContent)
      Updates the content of an existing enquiry made by the applicant.
      Parameters:
      applicant - The applicant requesting the edit.
      enquiryId - The ID of the enquiry to edit.
      newContent - The new content for the enquiry.

    • deleteEnquiry

      void deleteEnquiry(Applicant applicant, String enquiryId)
      Deletes an enquiry made by the applicant.
      Parameters:
      applicant - The applicant requesting the deletion.
      enquiryId - The ID of the enquiry to delete.

    • replyToEnquiry

      boolean replyToEnquiry(Enquiry enquiry, String response, String responderNRIC)
      Submits a reply to an enquiry.
      Parameters:
      enquiry - The enquiry being replied to.
      response - The reply content.
      responderNRIC - The NRIC of the responder.
      Returns:
      true if the reply was successfully submitted, false otherwise.
